	"interruptRitual.0": "Monty...?",
	"interruptRitual.1": "@! You almost ruined everything!$a#$b#I trusted you to help... why couldn't you trust me to know my own limits?$a",
	"interruptRitual.2": "I'm sorry... I should have listened to you.",
	"interruptRitual.3": "I did the right thing. You were in too much pain.",
