// FINCH HOUSE
	// monty 4 hearts - crow discovery, esther taunt
	"montyhearts4.0": "There's no sign of Monty... where is he?",
	"montyhearts4.1": "CAW!$6",
	"montyhearts4.2": "How did you get in here, you nosy little shit?$a#$b#Did Monty tell you that you could come over? $a#$b#Lovestruck little fool.$l",
	"montyhearts4.3": "You poor thing. You don't even know the secrets he keeps, do you?$u#$b#Wondering where he is? He's right behind you.$s",
	"montyhearts4.4": "He's a crow, honey. You didn't know? Oops.$h",
	"montyhearts4.5": "My sweet crow familiar.#$b#Too bad the little fool keeps falling in love with anyone who gives him the time of day.$u#$b#Oh well, he'll learn his lesson soon enough.$u",
	"montyhearts4.6": "Now scram, kid. You're trespassing.$a",
	
	// monty 7.3 hearts - with edwin
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.0": "Well... Here goes nothing.#$b#Edwin is up in the attic already getting things started. Are you sure you don't want to back out?",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.1": "Great.$h",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.2": "I have finished preparations for the ritual.#$b#Monty, are you sure you wish to proceed? I suspect it will be quite painful.$s",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.3": "Yes, I have to do this. I have to be free.$s",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.4": "@, I must impress upon you the importance of not interfering with the ritual.$s#$b#Even if Monty is in immense pain, any deviations could lead to things going horribly wrong. It's never wise to interrupt a spell once in progress.$s",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.5": "Monty, first you must drink the potion I've prepared. It will allow your form to solidify during the ritual.",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.6": "Blegh!$7",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.7": "(It is times like these that I do not miss my sense of taste.)#$b#@, you must hold the dragon's tooth above your head on my signal.#$b#I shall begin the spell now.",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.8": "Edwin begins to read aloud from his spellbook.",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.9": "Ugh... it feels like my bones are melting!$7#$b#No, don't stop!$s",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.10": "[Stop the ritual.]",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.11": "[Continue.]",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.12": "I know it is difficult to see Monty in pain...$s#$b#It shouldn't disrupt the ritual too much if you were to hold Monty's hand. It's almost over.",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.13": "Edwin continues chanting. The smoke is getting thicker.",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.14": "AUGH!$7",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.15": "Now, @!$7",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.16": "I feel...$s#$b#I feel great!$l",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.17": "The ritual was a success!$h",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.18": "Thank you guys so, so much!$l#$b#I have to... I have to go tell everyone!$l",
	"montyhearts7.3_edwin.19": "I know I can't possibly repay you, but anything you want, @, I'll give it to you, seriously.#$l",
	
	// monty 7.3 hearts - no edwin
	"montyhearts7.3_noEdwin.0": "Well... Here goes nothing.#$b#Are you sure you don't want to back out?",
	"montyhearts7.3_noEdwin.1": "Great.$h",
	"montyhearts7.3_noEdwin.2": "I got everything ready... you have the dragon tooth, right?#$b#Good. I'll start the spell, and when I tell you, use the dragon tooth.#$b#Also, no matter how much pain I'm in, you can't stop, okay? I *have* to do this. I have to be free.$s",
	"montyhearts7.3_noEdwin.3": "Monty begins to chant.",
	"montyhearts7.3_noEdwin.4": "Ugh... it feels like my bones are melting!$7#$b#No, we can't stop!$s",
	"montyhearts7.3_noEdwin.5": "[Stop the ritual.]",
	"montyhearts7.3_noEdwin.6": "[Continue.]",
	"montyhearts7.3_noEdwin.7": "Monty continues chanting. The smoke is getting thicker.",
	"montyhearts7.3_noEdwin.8": "AUGH!$7",
	"montyhearts7.3_noEdwin.9": "Now, @!",
	"montyhearts7.3_noEdwin.10": "I feel...$s#$b#I feel great!$l",
	"montyhearts7.3_noEdwin.11": "The ritual was a success!",
	"montyhearts7.3_noEdwin.12": "Thank you so, so much!$l#$b#I have to... I have to go tell everyone!",
	"montyhearts7.3_noEdwin.13": "I know I can't possibly repay you, but anything you want, @, I'll give it to you, seriously.#$l",

// LIBRARY
	// edwin 7 hearts - apology
	"edwinhearts7.0": "Oh, hello, @. I was just browsing the shelves for any books I haven't read yet.#$b#I don't suppose you have any recommendations?",
	"edwinhearts7.1": "What book would you recommend to Edwin?#Murder at Magnolia Mansion#My Life as a Teenage Werewolf#1001 Curses and Cures",
	"edwinhearts7.2": "Fascinating. I shall give it a try.",
	"edwinhearts7.3": "I'm glad we ran into each other, as it happens.#$b#This is... difficult for me to say, but...$s#$b#I apologize. I treated you quite rudely upon our first acquaintance... and for some time thereafter.$s",
